#. [message]: id=leader3,leader4,leader5,leader6
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:330
msgid ""
"Grr... nasty stinky-midgets. We know what you’re up to in there. We’ll be "
"back."
